snippet.title: ReCharge RC: High Voltage (Official Teaser Trailer)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3484640/ReCharge_RC_High_Voltage
Join the Discord! - https://discord.gg/XSdudfWjga
Follow the development on twitter! - https://x.com/hondune
Follow the development on TikTok! - https://www.tiktok.com/@hondunegames

Drift your way into ReCharge RC: High Voltage! Customize your vehicle, Create your very own race tracks, Share them online and race your friends best times with global online leaderboards. Created by an RC enthusiast, for RC enthusiasts!

More info coming soon, follow on discord, twitter, or TikTok to keep up with the latest updates! Join the Discord where I'm active daily and help shape the future of ReCharge RC! Help me make the best RC game ever!
